    <entry>
      <title>Markdown语法</title>
      <link href="/post/19236.html"/>
      <url>/post/19236.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>刚建的博客，布局还没完善(一堆Bug😵)，想着边学边记录一下，奈何Markdown语法还不会，我哭死😭😭😭<br>所以今天它来了，安排！！！(本来这应该作为我的第一篇博客的，但是懒得折腾啦😂)</p><h2 id="标题"><a href="#标题" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a>标题</h2><p><font color=yellow>注：</font>#后面有<strong><em>空格</em></strong></p><pre><code><figure class="highlight clean"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># h1</span><br><span class="line">## h2</span><br><span class="line">### h3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></code></pre><h2 id="换行"><a href="#换行" class="headerlink" title="换行"></a>换行</h2><p>在行末添加两个或两个以上的空格，然后按回车键即可创建一个换行符<code>&lt;br&gt;</code></p><h2 id="加粗、斜体"><a href="#加粗、斜体" class="headerlink" title="加粗、斜体"></a>加粗、斜体</h2><p>斜体用一个星号<code>*</code>包裹，粗体使用两个星号<code>**</code>包裹，粗斜体用三个星号<code>***</code>包裹，格式如下：<br>    <figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="strong">**我是粗体**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*我是斜体*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**<span class="emphasis">*我是粗斜体*</span>**</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h2 id="分割线、删除线、下划线"><a href="#分割线、删除线、下划线" class="headerlink" title="分割线、删除线、下划线"></a>分割线、删除线、下划线</h2><ol><li>分割线<br>可以用三个以上的星号、减号、底线建立分割线。同时也可以在星号或减号中间插入空格,格式如下： <figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">***</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>* *</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">- - -</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---------------</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>看我下面有分割线诶</li></ol><hr><ol><li><p>删除线<br> 只需在文本两端加入两个波浪线<code>~~</code>即可，格式如下：</p> <figure class="highlight haml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">~~我有删除线~~</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 效果：<del>我有删除线</del></p></li><li><p>下划线<br> 可通过HTML的<code>&lt;u&gt;</code>来实现，格式如下：</p> <figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">u</span>&gt;</span>我有下划线<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">u</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 效果：<u>我有下划线</u></p></li></ol><h2 id="代码样式"><a href="#代码样式" class="headerlink" title="代码样式"></a>代码样式</h2><ol><li>段落上实现代码样式<br> 只需加上 ` 将其代码包起来即可，格式如下： <figure class="highlight arcade"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">`我是代码`</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>代码块<br> 只需加上 ``` 将代码包起来，格式如下: <figure class="highlight arcade"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">``</span><span class="string">`我是代码块`</span><span class="string">``</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h2 id="链接和图片"><a href="#链接和图片" class="headerlink" title="链接和图片"></a>链接和图片</h2><ol><li>链接格式为<code>[链接名称](链接地址)</code>或直接使用地址<code>&lt;链接地址&gt;</code></li><li>图片格式为<code>![图片alt](图片地址 &quot;可选标题&quot;)</code></li></ol><h2 id="列表"><a href="#列表" class="headerlink" title="列表"></a>列表</h2><ul><li>无序列表使用星号<code>*</code>、加号<code>+</code>或者减号<code>-</code>,记得在此之后加上<font color=red>空格</font>，格式如下：  <figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span> 一号</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span> 二号</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span> 三号</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+</span> 一号</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+</span> 二号</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+</span> 三号</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 一号</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 二号</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 三号</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>有序列表使用数字加上<code>.</code>来显示，记得加上<font color=red>空格</font>，效果如代码样式的<code>1</code>和<code>2</code>,格式如下：  <figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1.</span> 一号</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2.</span> 二号</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">3.</span> 三号</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="表格"><a href="#表格" class="headerlink" title="表格"></a>表格</h2><p>使用<code>|</code>来分隔单元格，用<code>-</code>来分隔表头和内容，格式如下：<br>    <figure class="highlight gherkin"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">|<span class="string">表头</span>|<span class="string">表头</span>|</span><br><span class="line">|<span class="string">---</span>|<span class="string">---</span>|</span><br><span class="line">|<span class="string">单元格</span>|<span class="string">单元格</span>|</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><strong>对齐方式</strong></p><blockquote><p><code>-:</code>设置内容与表头右对齐<br><code>:-</code>设置内容与表头左对齐<br><code>:-:</code>设置内容与表头居中对齐</p></blockquote><pre><code><figure class="highlight gherkin"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">|<span class="string">居左</span>|<span class="string">居右</span>|<span class="string">居中</span>|</span><br><span class="line">|<span class="string">:---</span>|<span class="string">---:</span>|<span class="string">:---:</span>|</span><br><span class="line">|<span class="string">单元格</span>|<span class="string">单元格</span>|<span class="string">单元格</span>|</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></code></pre><h2 id="引用"><a href="#引用" class="headerlink" title="引用"></a>引用</h2><p>在段落前加入<code>&gt;</code>符号即可<br>格式：<code>&gt;这是引用的内容</code><br>效果如下：</p><blockquote><p>这是引用的内容</p></blockquote><h3 id="多个段落的引用"><a href="#多个段落的引用" class="headerlink" title="多个段落的引用"></a>多个段落的引用</h3><p>当有多个段落时，在段落之间空白行添加<code>&gt;</code>，格式如下：<br><figure class="highlight node-repl"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;第一段</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;第二段</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>效果如下：</p><blockquote><p>第一段</p><p>第二段</p></blockquote><h3 id="嵌套快引用以及其他元素的引用"><a href="#嵌套快引用以及其他元素的引用" class="headerlink" title="嵌套快引用以及其他元素的引用"></a>嵌套快引用以及其他元素的引用</h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;第一段</span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt;&gt;第二段</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt;- 我是<span class="strong">**<span class="emphasis">*列表*</span>**</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果：</p><blockquote><p>第一段</p><blockquote><p>第二段</p></blockquote><ul><li>我是<strong><em>列表</em></strong></li></ul></blockquote><h2 id="脚注"><a href="#脚注" class="headerlink" title="脚注"></a>脚注</h2><p>格式：<code>[^我是脚注]</code><br>效果：别看了<sup><a href="#fn_我是脚注" id="reffn_我是脚注">我是脚注</a></sup>    </p><h2 id="Emoji表情"><a href="#Emoji表情" class="headerlink" title="Emoji表情"></a>Emoji表情</h2><p>语法：<code>:smile:</code><br>效果：😄（我是复制过来的，用语法不知道在vscode上编辑为啥没用）<br>或直接从<a href="https://gist.github.com/rxaviers/7360908">这里</a>复制粘贴</p><h2 id="结束语"><a href="#结束语" class="headerlink" title="结束语"></a>结束语</h2><p>基本语法完结撒花！！！</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Markdown </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>最新文章图标的实现</title>
      <link href="/post/2263.html"/>
      <url>/post/2263.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="步骤"><a href="#步骤" class="headerlink" title="步骤"></a>步骤</h2><p>找到主题配置文件<code>_config.butterfly.yml</code></p><pre><code>1. 找到`beautify`,将`enable`设为`true`,`title-prefix-icon`设为：`&#39;\f863&#39;`<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">beautify:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">field:</span> <span class="string">post</span> <span class="comment"># site/post</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">title-prefix-icon:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;\f863&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">title-prefix-icon-color:</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>2. 找到`inject`的`head`引入如下文件：<figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">inject:</span><br><span class="line">    head:</span><br><span class="line">        - &quot;<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="language-css"><span class="selector-id">#article-container</span><span class="selector-class">.post-content</span> <span class="selector-tag">h1</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:before</span>, <span class="selector-tag">h2</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:before</span>, <span class="selector-tag">h3</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:before</span>, <span class="selector-tag">h4</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:before</span>, <span class="selector-tag">h5</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:before</span>, <span class="selector-tag">h6</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:before</span> &#123; -webkit-<span class="attribute">animation</span>: avatar_turn_around <span class="number">1s</span> linear infinite; -moz-<span class="attribute">animation</span>: avatar_turn_around <span class="number">1s</span> linear infinite; -o-<span class="attribute">animation</span>: avatar_turn_around <span class="number">1s</span> linear infinite; -ms-<span class="attribute">animation</span>: avatar_turn_around <span class="number">1s</span> linear infinite; <span class="attribute">animation</span>: avatar_turn_around <span class="number">1s</span> linear infinite; &#125;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span>&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></code></pre><h2 id="最后"><a href="#最后" class="headerlink" title="最后"></a>最后</h2><pre><code>在`blog`根目录下输入：`hexo cl &amp;&amp; hexo g -d` 就可以查看效果啦</code></pre><blockquote><p>参考<a href="https://cnhuazhu.top/butterfly/2021/02/24/Hexo%E9%AD%94%E6%94%B9/Hexo%E5%B0%8F%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98%E6%97%8B%E8%BD%AC%E9%A3%8E%E8%BD%A6%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE/">花猪</a></p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
      
